In episode 143, Jack & Miles are joined by comedian Dani Fernandez to discuss the Hawaii volcano eruption, the Met Gala looks, Menghazi with Eric Schneiderman, Melania Trump copying Michelle Obama yet again, the NRA hiring Oliver North as their president, plus producer Anna joins to discuss the Iran Nuclear Deal and what can happen now that Trump has pulled out, & more!
